 (2091,3,'\"Intelligence without character is a dangerous thing.\"\r\n-- G. Steinem\r\n'),
 (2092,3,'\"It says he made us all to be just like him.  So if we\'re dumb, then god is\r\ndumb, and maybe even a little ugly on the side.\"\r\n-- Frank Zappa\r\n'),
