 (2144,3,'How many Zen Buddhist does it take to change a light bulb?\r\n\r\nTwo.  One to change it and one not to change it.\r\n'),
 (2145,3,'\"I prefer the blunted cudgels of the followers of the Serpent God.\"\r\n-- Sean Doran the Younger\r\n'),
