 (3296,4,'The Sixth Commandment of Frisbee:\r\n	The greatest single aid to distance is for the disc to be going in a\r\n	direction you did not want.   (Goes the wrong way = Goes a long way.)\r\n		-- Dan Roddick\r\n'),
