 (3361,4,'When asked the definition of \"pi\":\r\nThe Mathematician:\r\n	Pi is the number expressing the relationship between the\r\n	circumference of a circle and its diameter.\r\nThe Physicist:\r\n	Pi is 3.1415927, plus or minus 0.000000005.\r\nThe Engineer:\r\n	Pi is about 3.\r\n'),
